{"tid":2434509,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「劉公子」驚螫鵝頸橋「打小人」 現場發現多張高官照片","createTime":"2021-03-05T14:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T22:58:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"34366363818964bf185793cd1c2a164ef7ddeb70","tid":2434509,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:42:24.000Z","msg":"今天（5日）是中國24節氣「驚螫」，有不少市民按傳統習俗到銅鑼灣鵝頸橋底「打小人」，希望今年事事順利。記者晚上8時許到達鵝頸橋底已見人頭湧湧，在疫情下打小人路邊檔前仍約有200名市民排隊。<br />\n<br />\n60多歲檔主接受探訪時表示今年客人多數祈求「身體健康」、「趕走疫情」及「工作順利」等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/189389/FB%E8%A3%BD%E5%9C%96%E6%A9%AB005@1200x1200.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F189389%2FFB%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%25A9%25AB005%401200x1200.jpeg&h=d72e78d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場市民劉公子稱他專程來打小人，因昨天47人的聆訊結果令他「一肚氣」又「喊餐飽」，必須來消消氣。他心目中有六名「小人」但不便開名，但港人應該不難猜到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/189391/FB%E8%A3%BD%E5%9C%96%E6%A9%AB001@1200x1200.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F189391%2FFB%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%25A9%25AB001%401200x1200.jpeg&h=b81b2990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者現場所見地上留下不少高官的照片，包括：張建宗、李惠琼、鄧炳強等。有街坊表示今年有較年輕的市民來打小人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/189392/FB%E8%A3%BD%E5%9C%96%E6%A9%AB003@1200x1200.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F189392%2FFB%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%25A9%25AB003%401200x1200.jpeg&h=76fa2b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/189393/FB%E8%A3%BD%E5%9C%96%E6%A9%AB002@1200x1200.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F189393%2FFB%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%25A9%25AB002%401200x1200.jpeg&h=c8d45723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2位年輕市民今年第一次來「打小人」，原因是今年社會上整體環境及對未來生活的期望都較差，雖然打小人這個儀式不知道是否有助實現願望，但仍想給自己一個小希望，給自己多點正能量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2021-03-05/18205141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2021-03-05%2F18205141&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedZ4O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=9bdb4b40\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2021-03-05/18205141</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.share.photo.xuite.net/doublepp2004/12c33b7/17855188/968019939_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.share.photo.xuite.net%2Fdoublepp2004%2F12c33b7%2F17855188%2F968019939_m.jpg&h=1a646853&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9231b3552c548e2ead76f242db07301838c2b693","tid":2434509,"uid":44209,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jc5SBZd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjc5SBZd.gif&h=95fb9eb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a11e5ee19c3e7b2ebc9ac2c0af6d86202e7fb573","tid":2434509,"uid":50744,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:49:15.000Z","msg":"翠翠都有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec3bff09fe5b314bc2c9668e014d9c61df35c44","tid":2434509,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370f82f0de8975e353e1a63be53ee367a2dff199","tid":2434509,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ffc7d57f2225f105a142d5949af96d608d8f10","tid":2434509,"uid":58627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:54:07.000Z","msg":"冇吳樂俊？"},{"pid":"d06abb105bfea75245db5